name: Validate policy counter number sequencing for Fed Ex Ground Program (Renewal)

testSteps.description: Given underwriter has converted  quote to policy for LOB Workers Compensation
And with the underwriting company 'Protective Insurance Company'
And with Program as 'Fed Ex Ground'
And underwriter fills in required details
And underwriter chooses to Save and Continue
Then the policy form number should be shown generated as '2100000025-02'
